        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[大陆一架无人机两架歼10进入台湾西南防空识别区]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台湾国防部称，中国大陆解放军一架无人机、两架歼10战机进入台湾西南防空识别区，持续在台海周边活动。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>综合《联合报》</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>《自由时报》</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>报道，台国防部</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>星期天（11月20日）</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>发布解放军动态。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台国防部称，从星期六（11月19日）6时至20日6时为止，台军侦获大陆军机10架次，大陆军舰三艘次，持续在台海周边活动。其中有一架次BZK-007无人机、两架次歼10战机进入西南防空识别区。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台军称，“BZK-007”无人侦察机由福建、广东交界处的外海，飞入台湾防空识别区西南空域再飞返。两架“歼10”战机则是由东沙岛东北方空域飞入台湾防空识别区。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>台国防部说，台军运用任务机、舰及岸置导弹系统严密监控与应处。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


