      <figcaption>北京市11月19日出现一例冠病死亡病例。图为防疫人员11月18日在北京某居民小区门口处理垃圾。（路透社）</figcaption>
       
            

<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>中国首都北京市星期天（11月20日）通报一例冠病死亡病例。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据北京市卫健委通报，死亡病例为87岁的男性，他11月11日出现干咳症状，11月13日诊断为轻型冠病，11月19日病情恶化，因严重肺部细菌感染，发生脓毒症休克，经抢救无效死亡。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>彭博社的报道称，这是中国大陆官方近</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>6个月以来通报的第一例冠病死亡病例，上一个死亡病例在今年5月26日报告。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>北京市最近疫情升温，星期六共新增69例本土确诊病例和552例无症状感染者。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据中国国家卫健委官网，中国大陆19日</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>新增确诊</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>本土</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>病例</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>2204例，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>新增本土无症状感染者</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>2万2011例</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


